cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Gemma4Defense-2B: A Compact CTI Specialist Fine-Tuned from Gemma-4-E2B-it"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Mulia
    given-names: Samuel
    alias: athena129
date-released: 2026-05-07
url: "https://github.com/GPT-64590/Gemma4Defense-2B"
